oing to look for a new job as soon as his firm asks him to come back to the=
 office.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height:=
 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">If you choose to Return, you&#8217;re essentiall=
y making a bet that the benefits of all being in the same office every day =
outweighs the risks of attracting lesser talent and potentially losing your=
